%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tim%20Cook%20had%20bold%20visions%20for%20Apple.%20See%20which%20ones%20came%20true.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223588%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tim%20Cook%20speaking%20during%20a%20presentation%20in%20front%20of%20cursive%20%26quot%3BApple%26quot%3B%20letters%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e794c3a98bc8fdc096cf33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222691%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20prominence%20of%20augmented%20reality%20and%20tablets%20were%20among%20Tim%20Cook's%20predictions%20during%20his%20leadership%20at%20Apple.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Gress%20Media%20Inc%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EApple's%20outgoing%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20had%20ambitious%20plans%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20predicted%20that%20tablets%20would%20overtake%20PCs%20and%20that%20smartwatches%20would%20replace%20car%20keys.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20of%20his%20predictions%20and%20visions%20for%20Apple%20came%20true%2C%20while%20others%20were%20never%20fully%20realized.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-cook-memes-jokes-stepping-down-apple-ceo-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETim%20Cook%20steps%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20Apple's%20CEO%20on%20September%201%2C%20he'll%20have%20spent%2015%20years%20as%20the%20company's%20chief%20executive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20time%20marked%20significant%20growth%20and%20innovation%20for%20the%20company%2C%20its%20value%20ballooning%20from%20%24350%20billion%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-stock-price-returns-explained-under-ceo-tim-cook-buybacks-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eto%20%244%20trillion%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Products%20like%20the%20AirPods%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-apple-watch%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple%20Watch%3C%2Fa%3E%20became%20commonplace%20in%20daily%20life%20globally.%20As%20for%20the%20iPhone%2C%20the%20year%20Cook%20became%20CEO%2C%20the%20company%20was%20selling%2072%20million%20a%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2026%2F04%2F21%2Fbusiness%2Fhow-apple-became-a-4-trillion-company-under-tim-cook.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20Now%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3De8649d1e753322f9815dcfde772cb24f89ac1777b01387588412c3af6e4d5c12%26postID%3D69e785cbd17822f7a32f890a%26postSlug%3Dtim-cook-visions-predictions-for-apple-2026-4%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.apple.com%252Fnewsroom%252F2026%252F01%252Fapple-reports-first-quarter-results%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20says%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20has%202.5%20billion%20active%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202011%2C%20Cook%20took%20over%20from%20Steve%20Jobs%2C%20the%20Apple%20cofounder%20who%20had%20overseen%20the%20company%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-company-history-photos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elaunching%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20in%20a%20garage%20in%20the%201970s.%20When%20Cook%20assumed%20the%20chief%20executive%20role%2C%20Apple%20had%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Ftexas%2Fnews%2Fapple-passes-exxon-as-most-valuable-u-s-company%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epassed%20Exxon%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20most%20valuable%20public%20company%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20the%20iPhone%204s%20was%20about%20to%20be%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20time%20as%20CEO%2C%20some%20of%20Cook's%20bets%20paid%20off%2C%20others%20were%20only%20partly%20realized%2C%20and%20others%20still%20have%20a%20way%20to%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESee%20which%20of%20Cook's%20tech%20predictions%20and%20visions%20for%20Apple%20came%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEven%20before%20Tim%20Cook%20took%20over%20as%20CEO%2C%20he%20made%20statements%20about%20Apple's%20future.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224663%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tim%20Cook%20and%20Steve%20Jobs%20talking%20next%20to%20each%20other.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7ac56367066d7c296f268%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223497%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECook%20served%20as%20chief%20operating%20officer%20before%20assuming%20Jobs'%20executive%20role.%3Cp%3EKimberly%20White%2FCorbis%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20becoming%20Apple's%20chief%20executive%2C%20Cook%2C%20who%20joined%20Apple%20in%201998%2C%20served%20as%20the%20company's%20chief%20operating%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20took%20over%20Jobs'%20role%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20while%20the%20co-founder%20was%20on%20medical%20leave%2C%20handling%20day-to-day%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202009%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20iPad's%20launch%20the%20following%20year%2C%20Jobs%20stayed%20radio%20silent%20on%20the%20mysterious%20tablet.%20Cook%2C%20however%2C%20hinted%20that%20the%20company%20was%20working%20on%20something%20%26quot%3Bvery%20innovative%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Guardian%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2009%2Faug%2F23%2Fapple-tablet-steve-jobs-touchscreen%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20iPad%20was%20a%20mega%20hit%20upon%20its%20release%20and%2C%2010%20years%20after%20its%20launch%2C%20surpassed%20500%20million%20total%20sales%2C%20Cook%20said%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnet.com%2Ftech%2Fmobile%2Fapple-says-its-sold-over-500-million-ipads%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook%20officially%20became%20CEO%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%202010%2C%20Cook%20said%20Apple%20would%20continue%20to%20invest%20in%20its%20Apple%20TV%20streaming%20device%20because%20%26quot%3Bour%20gut%20tells%20us%20there's%20something%20there.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20people%20watching%20a%20television%20with%20the%20Apple%20TV%20logo%20on%20the%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7af1d3fecbb42897a236f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhile%20Apple%20has%20largely%20stayed%20true%20to%20Cook's%20word%20in%202010%2C%20rumors%20of%20an%20Apple%20television%20have%20occasionally%20surfaced.%3Cp%3EFrame%20Stock%20Footage%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20the%20streaming%20boom%20was%20just%20about%20to%20begin.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-history-streaming-growth-story-hollywood-disruption-subscribers-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENetflix%3C%2Fa%3E%20launched%20its%20streaming-only%20plan%20in%20November%20that%20year%2C%20eliminating%20the%20DVD-by-mail%20requirement%20to%20access%20the%20streaming%20service.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fhulu-bundles%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHulu%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20launched%20its%20subscription%20plan%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flive-apple-coo-tim-cook-at-the-goldman-tech-conference-2010-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202010%20that%20Apple%20would%20steer%20clear%20of%20manufacturing%20its%20own%20TVs%2C%20instead%20focusing%20on%20its%20Apple%20TV%20line%20of%20streaming%20boxes.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20he%20referred%20to%20the%20Apple%20TV%20streaming%20devices%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bhobby%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20pledged%20the%20company's%20continued%20interest%20because%20%26quot%3Bour%20gut%20tells%20us%20there's%20something%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook's%20and%20Apple's%20hunch%20proved%20to%20be%20right.%20The%20streaming%20industry%20continued%20to%20grow%2C%20and%20in%20December%202025%2C%20made%20up%20nearly%20half%20of%20all%20TV%20viewing%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nielsen.com%2Fnews-center%2F2026%2Fstreaming-shatters-multiple-records-in-december-2025-with-47-5-of-tv-viewing-according-to-nielsens-the-gauge%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENielsen%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20continued%20its%20line%20of%20streaming%20devices%20and%20launched%20its%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-shows-streaming-on-apple-tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estreaming%20service%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%202013%2C%20Cook%20predicted%20that%20tablets%20would%20overtake%20PCs.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222430%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tim%20Cook%20using%20an%20iPad.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7b0223fecbb42897a237c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221823%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETim%20Cook's%20prediction%20of%20the%20importance%20of%20tablets%20reflect's%20Apple's%20attention%20to%20the%20iPad.%3Cp%3EScott%20Olson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECook%20made%20enthusiastic%20predictions%20for%20tablets%2C%20saying%20in%202013%20that%20tablets%20would%20outsell%20PCs%20within%20two%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2013%2F9%2F21%2F4755852%2Fapple-ceo-tim-cook-full-bloomberg-businessweek-interview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Verge%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Cook's%20prediction%20was%20largely%20true%20for%20Apple%20%E2%80%94%20the%20iPad%20has%20been%20a%20bigger%20seller%20than%20the%20iMac%20since%20its%20launch%20%E2%80%94%20PCs%20have%20still%20held%20their%20own%20against%20tablets%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%202021%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2F2024%2Fcomputer-internet-use-2021.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECensus%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%2081%25%20of%20US%20households%20owned%20a%20computer%2C%20while%2064%25%20owned%20a%20tablet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHe%20also%20had%20bold%20predictions%20for%20smartwatches.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223624%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tim%20Cook%20giving%20a%20presentation%20in%20front%20of%20an%20Apple%20Watch%20on%20screen%20behind%20him.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7b122a98bc8fdc096d004%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222718%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETim%20Cook%20hailed%20the%20Apple%20Watch%20as%20a%20life-changing%20piece%20of%20technology.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Apple%20Watch%20was%20unveiled%20in%202015%2C%20Cook%20predicted%20the%20device%20would%20start%20to%20replace%20common%20items%2C%20such%20as%20car%20keys%2C%20in%20people's%20everyday%20lives%2C%20TechCrunch%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2015%2F02%2F27%2Ftim-cook-says-apple-watch-could-replace-your-car-keys-and-thats-just-the-start%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20product's%20reviews%20upon%20release%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-watch-reviews-are-bad-2015-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eweren't%20all%20positive%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Apple%20would%20carve%20out%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20the%20smartwatch%20market%20long%20term.%20Per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsqmagazine.co.uk%2Fsmartwatch-statistics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESQ%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Apple%20had%20a%2028%25%20global%20market%20share%20for%20smartwatches%20in%202025%2C%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-us%2F118271%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunlock%20your%20car%20using%20your%20Apple%20Watch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20provided%20the%20car%20is%20compatible%2C%20and%20you%20have%20an%20Apple%20Watch%20Series%205%20or%20later%2C%20or%20an%20Apple%20Watch%20SE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWearables%20as%20a%20whole%20became%20part%20of%20Cook's%20and%20Apple's%20strategy%20in%20the%20decade.%20The%20following%20year%2C%20the%20company%20released%20its%20AirPods%20Bluetooth%20earbuds%2C%20selling%20over%2014%20million%20in%20the%20product's%20first%20full%20year%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fgreatspeculations%2F2020%2F01%2F21%2Fhow-apples-airpods-business-compares-with-initial-sales-of-the-iphone--ipad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECook%20said%2C%20a%20little%20prematurely%2C%20%26quot%3B2015%20will%20be%20the%20year%20of%20Apple%20Pay.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225973%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20phone%20holds%20up%20Apple%20Pay%20to%20a%20payment%20machine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7b1fc367066d7c296f29e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20Pay%20is%20now%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20digital%20wallets%20in%20the%20US.%3Cp%3EDenPhotos%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20full%20year%20after%20Apple%20launched%20its%20mobile%20payment%20service%2C%20its%20CEO%20made%20an%20ambitious%20statement%20about%20its%20immediate%20use%20and%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-pay%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApple%20Pay%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20a%20bit%20of%20time%20to%20get%20off%20the%20ground%2C%20but%20over%2011%20years%20after%20its%20launch%2C%20it's%20grown%20into%20the%20most%20popular%20digital%20wallet%20in%20the%20US%2C%20alongside%20PayPal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcapitaloneshopping.com%2Fresearch%2Fapple-pay-statistics%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECapitalOne%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20over%2090%25%20of%20US%20retailers%20accept%20Apple%20Pay%2C%20and%20the%20service%20is%20used%20in%2014.2%25%20of%20all%20online%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%202016%2C%20Cook%20said%20he%20believed%20%26quot%3Ba%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20population%26quot%3B%20would%20eventually%20use%20augmented%20reality%20technology%20every%20day.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222141%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Tim%20Cook%20Memoji%20displays%20on%20a%20phone%20screen%20during%20a%20presentation.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7b2b9a98bc8fdc096d019%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221606%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20has%20implemented%20AR%20technology%20like%20Memoji%20into%20its%20products.%3Cp%3EJOSH%20EDELSON%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20mid%202010s%2C%20Cook%20has%20been%20a%20strong%20advocate%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanufacturer-augmented-reality-vpn-zero-trust-network-for-connection-collaboration-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaugmented%20reality%20(AR)%3C%2Fa%3E%20technology.%20In%202016%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-ceo-tim-cook-explains-augmented-reality-2016-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elikened%20the%20technology's%20potential%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20one%20of%20the%20most%20basic%20routines%20of%20daily%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20think%20that%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20the%20population%20of%20developed%20countries%2C%20and%20eventually%20all%20countries%2C%20will%20have%20AR%20experiences%20every%20day%2C%20almost%20like%20eating%20three%20meals%20a%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Cook%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%20to%20tout%20AR's%20importance%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%20In%202022%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20really%20going%20to%20look%20back%20and%20think%20about%20how%20we%20once%20lived%20without%20AR%2C%26quot%3B%20CNBC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2022%2F10%2F03%2Fapple-ceo-tim-cook-doesnt-like-metaverse-prefers-augmented-reality.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO's%20confidence%20in%20the%20technology%20came%20as%20competitors%20began%20to%20invest%20heavily%20in%20virtual%20reality%20(VR).%20Meta's%20%26quot%3BHorizon%20Worlds%26quot%3B%20offered%20a%20full%20VR%20experience%20for%20users%2C%20but%20Cook%20talked%20down%20the%20technology%20and%20affirmed%20that%20Apple%20would%20be%20putting%20its%20eggs%20in%20the%20AR%20basket.%20(Last%20month%2C%20Meta%20announced%20it%20would%20wind%20down%20the%20%26quot%3BHorizon%20Worlds%26quot%3B%20VR%20experience%2C%20before%20swiftly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2026%2F03%2F19%2Fmeta-backtracks-on-decision-to-end-horizon-worlds-vr-ans-spoke-up.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclarifying%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20would%20remain.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20has%20incorporated%20AR%20technology%20into%20its%20products%2C%20from%20Memoji%20avatars%20to%20practical%20uses%20like%20the%20iPhone's%20%26quot%3BMeasure%26quot%3B%20app.%20Apple's%20proprietary%20ARKit%20framework%20enables%20third-party%20developers%20to%20create%20AR%20apps%20for%20Apple%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsqmagazine.co.uk%2Faugmented-reality-statistics%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESQ%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%2C%20in%202025%2C%20approximately%2060%25%20of%20Americans%20use%20AR.%20Each%20day%2C%20as%20many%20as%20500%20million%20users%20engage%20with%20AR%20filters%20and%20lenses%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eon%20platforms%20such%20as%20Instagram%20and%20Snapchat%2C%20it%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%202024%2C%20Cook%20called%20Apple%20Vision%20Pro%20headset%20%26quot%3Btomorrow's%20technology%20today.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226380%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tim%20Cook%20poses%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bpeace%26quot%3B%20sign%20next%20to%20an%20Apple%20Vision%20Pro%20headset.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7b40a367066d7c296f2b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224785%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETim%20Cook%20embraced%20AR%20technology%20while%20leading%20Apple.%3Cp%3EPhilip%20Pacheco%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20Apple's%20biggest%20AR%20endeavor%20was%20the%20Apple%20Vision%20Pro%20headset%2C%20released%20in%202024.%20The%20mixed-reality%20headset%20uses%20AR%20to%20combine%20users'%20surroundings%20with%20digital%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20released%2C%20Cook%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Btomorrow's%20technology%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fappleinsider.com%2Farticles%2F24%2F02%2F02%2Fapple-vision-pro-is-tomorrows-technology-today-says-tim-cook%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAppleInsider%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20device%20was%20met%20with%20mixed%20reviews%2C%20Cook%20and%20Apple%20remain%20undeterred%20in%20their%20wearable-technology%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20reportedly%20developing%20smart%20glasses%2C%20which%20will%20look%20to%20rival%20a%20similar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fray-ban-meta-smart-glasses-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20product%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECook's%20boldest%20vision%20for%20Apple%20was%20its%20role%20in%20the%20health%20sector%2C%20a%20goal%20it's%20still%20pursuing.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224494%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tim%20Cook%20giving%20a%20presentation%20with%20the%20health%20app%20on%20screen%20behind%20him.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7b4e5367066d7c296f2d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223370%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETim%20Cook%20once%20said%20%26quot%3BApple's%20greatest%20contribution%20to%20mankind%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20in%20regards%20to%20health.%3Cp%3EStephen%20Lam%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20CEO%20said%20that%20in%20the%20future%2C%20people%20will%20look%20back%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BApple's%20most%20important%20contribution%20to%20mankind%20has%20been%20in%20health.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHealth%20monitoring%20has%20already%20been%20a%20part%20of%20the%20company's%20strategy%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20with%20the%20Apple%20Watch%20offering%20fitness%20and%20cardiovascular%20health%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20the%20company%20is%20developing%20new%20AI-powered%20health%20features%2C%20which%20some%20have%20called%20an%20%26quot%3BAI%20doctor.%26quot%3B%20While%20Apple%20has%20since%20scaled%20back%20these%20plans%2C%20it's%20still%20planning%20to%20integrate%20some%20of%20the%20new%20features%20into%20its%20health%20app%2C%20Bloomberg%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1VHSL0KhhmuVJzKAHbX-NXAhdSiJE9GOYl38kvx1liMM%2Fedit%3Ftab%3Dt.0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20business%20has%20always%20been%20about%20enriching%20people's%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20Cook%20said%20of%20Apple's%20role%20in%20health%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-cook-visions-predictions-for-apple-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776959675000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e9326a3fecbb42897a2e18%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-cook-visions-predictions-for-apple-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20augmented%20reality%20to%20Apple's%20role%20in%20health%2C%20Ti