0for%20Princeton%2C%20told%20the%20lawyers%20in%20the%20case%20that%20their%20high-profile%20clients%20should%20not%20expect%20special%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20March%20hearing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2026-03-13%2Felon-musk-s-ketamine-use-can-t-be-probed-in-openai-fraud-trial%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20by%20Bloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20judge%20said%20the%20trial%20witnesses%20%E2%80%94%20a%20list%20that%20includes%20Musk%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ceo-satya-nadella-ai-revolution-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft's%20Satya%20Nadella%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Mira%20Murati%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-attracts-more-thinking-machines-lab-talent-in-ai-shakeup-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThinking%20Machines%20Lab%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20will%20enter%20the%20courthouse%20through%20the%20public%20entrance.%20She%20also%20instructed%20the%20parties%20to%20pick%20up%20the%20tab%20for%20the%20jury's%20lunch%20during%20deliberations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20plenty%20of%20money%20to%20pay%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20the%20expense%2C%20which%20is%20usually%20covered%20by%20taxpayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20who've%20practiced%20before%20her%20say%20this%20is%20par%20for%20the%20course%20for%20Gonzalez%20Rogers%2C%20who%20is%20known%20for%20running%20a%20tight%20ship%20and%20is%20watchful%20of%20her%20jurors'%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe's%20a%20tough%20judge%2C%20and%20she%20knows%20that%20the%20public's%20time%20is%20precious%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20criminal%20defense%20lawyer%20Shaffy%20Moeel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20federal%20judge%20in%20Oakland%2C%20appointed%20by%20then-President%20Barack%20Obama%20in%202011%2C%20she%20is%20known%20for%20her%20command%20of%20the%20courtroom%2C%20wrangling%20unruly%20lawyers%20or%20schooling%20them%