%20of%20Texas%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20Contra%20Costa%20Times%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGonzalez%20Rogers%20went%20to%20Princeton%2C%20cleaning%20and%20cutting%20grass%20during%20breaks%20to%20help%20pay%20her%20tuition%2C%20former%20US%20Sen.%20Diane%20Feinstein%20told%20Congress%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduating%20from%20law%20school%20at%20UC%20Berkeley%2C%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20litigator%20at%20Cooley%20and%20in%201998%20became%20its%20first%20Latina%20partner.%20In%202008%2C%20California%20Gov.%20Arnold%20Schwarzenegger%20appointed%20her%20an%20Alameda%20County%20Superior%20Court%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk's%20trial%20against%20Altman%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-sues-sam-altman-betrays-openai-mission-chatgpt-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eover%20OpenAI's%20transition%20to%20a%20for-profit%3C%2Fa%3E%20entity%2C%20starts%20on%20April%2027%20with%20jury%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGonzalez%20Rogers%20will%20solely%20preside%20over%20what%20may%20prove%20to%20be%20the%20fiercest%20battle%20of%20the%20case%20%E2%80%94%20how%20OpenAI%20should%20be%20held%20accountable%20should%20the%20jury%20find%20OpenAI%20cofounders%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-vs-openai-sam-altman-legal-battle-stakes-microsoft-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAltman%2C%20liable%20for%20deceiving%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20its%20for-profit%20plans%20before%20he%20left%20the%20company%20he%20cofounded%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20asked%20the%20judge%20to%20consider%20removing%20Altman%20as%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20for-profit%20entity%2C%20among%20other%20requests%20that%20could%20change%20the%20face%20of%20the%20ChatGPT%20maker%20and%20Wall%20Street's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-ipo-public-offering-ai-chatgpt-microsoft-sam-altman-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehopes%20for%20an%20IPO%3C