0to%20stop%20charging%20developers%20fees%20for%20sales%20made%20outside%20the%20App%20Store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20contempt%20of%20court%20order%20against%20Apple%2C%20she%20accused%20the%20company's%20vice%20president%20of%20finance%2C%20Alex%20Roman%2C%20of%20lying%20under%20oath%20in%20the%20case.%20She%20also%20called%20out%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%2C%20saying%20he%20ignored%20advice%20from%20Apple's%20Phillip%20Schiller%20that%20the%20company%20comply%20with%20the%20court's%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCook%20chose%20poorly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20of%20referring%20the%20case%20to%20the%20US%20Attorney%20for%20the%20Northern%20District%20of%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20didn't%20return%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Musk%20v.%20Altman%20fight%20could%20also%20get%20messy.%20Gonzalez%20Rogers%20has%20already%20called%20out%20lawyers%20on%20both%20sides%20for%20overlitigating%20the%20case%20on%20behalf%20of%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-sam-altman-openai-nonprofit-attorneys-skeptical-california-court-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebillionaire%20clients%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20court%20will%20not%20waste%20precious%20judicial%20resources%20on%20the%20parties'%20gamesmanship%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20a%202025%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20who%20know%20Gonzalez%20Rogers%20told%20Business%20Insider%20to%20expect%20more%20such%20missives%20as%20the%20case%20intensifies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20easy%20to%20manage%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20that'll%20be%20too%20much%20of%20a%20problem%20for%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Christopher%20Arriola%2C%20a%20former%20local%20prosecutor%20who%20has%20known%20the%20judge%20for%2025%20years.%20%26quot%3BShe%20won't%20put%20up%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20bluster%20or%20nonsense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22ht