0Campbell%20and%20Mitchell%20Robertson%20play%20younger%20versions%20of%20their%20characters.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CI%20sometimes%20just%20feel%20an%20impulse%20to%20write%20about%20something.%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Marta%20Balaga%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20top%20doctor%20says%20don't%20use%20fitness%20trackers%2C%20but%20is%20obsessed%20with%20one%20health%20metric%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227952%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20running%20in%20the%20street.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ea1c983fecbb42897a3198%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Ewera%20Rodsawang%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMeasuring%20our%20health%20data%20with%20wearable%20tech%20is%20more%20popular%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDr.%20Suzanne%20O'Sullivan%20tracks%20her%20step%20count%2C%20but%20said%20healthy%20people%20shouldn't%20buy%20into%20other%20metrics.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20healthier%20to%20listen%20to%20your%20body's%20cues%20and%20get%20checked%20out%20if%20you're%20worried%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-fitness-trackers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFitness%20trackers%3C%2Fa%3E%20aren't%20worth%20your%20money%2C%20a%20top%20doctor%20with%2030%20years%20of%20clinical%20experience%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20does%20have%20one%20exception%20to%20this%20rule%3A%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnot-retiring-work-healthy-aging-walking-splits-community-diet-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estep%20count%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20a%20fitness%20tracker%2C%20but%20I%20am%20obsessed%20with%20my%20step%20count%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Suzanne%20O'Sullivan%2C%20the%20author%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Age%20of%20Diagnosis%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20explores%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20of%20receiving%20a%20medical%20diagnosis%2C%20told%20the%20April%2013%20episode%20of%20the%20Intelligence%20Squared%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20it%20just%20encourages%20me%20to%20make%20sure%20I'm%20a%20little%20bit%20active%20every%20day.%20Choose%20wisely%20what%20you%20monitor%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20O'Sullivan%2C%20a%20consultant%20neurologist%20at%20the%20National%20Hospital%20for%20Neurology%20and%20Neurosurgery%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224464ced9-ad0a-4ce1-b265-e2ee1474a8f5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealthy%20people%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20constantly%20aware%20of%20metrics%20like%20their%20heart%20rate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EO'Sullivan%20said%20that%20a%20healthy%20person%20doesn't%20need%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20automatic%20bodily%20processes%20like%20sleep%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbryan-johnson-says-resting-heart-rate-is-key-health-indicator-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheart%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20digestion%2C%20partly%20because%20our%20bodies%20change%20all%20the%20time.%20Every%20run%20up%20the%20stairs%20will%20raise%20our%20heart%20rate%2C%20as%20each%20bite%20of%20food%20will%20cause%20the%20bowels%20to%20move%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20trackers%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-i-stopped-wearing-my-smartwatch-at-work-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmart%20watches%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20rings%20make%20us%20aware%20of%20these%20normal%20changes%2C%20interpreting%20the%20data%20without%20the%20guidance%20of%20a%20qualified%20medical%20professional%20can%20be%20unnecessarily%20confusing%20and%20stressful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBodily%20process%20%26quot%3Bare%20happening%20at%20a%20level%20that%20we%20don't%20really%20notice%20them%20when%20we're%20healthy.%20And%20that's%20the%20best%20way%20for%20them%20to%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20O'Sullivan%20wants%20people%20to%20focus%20on%20how%20they%20feel%20rather%20than%20what%20their%20tracker%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20worry%20about%20how%20many%20hours%20you%20slept.%20If%20you%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20morning%20and%20you're%20refreshed%20and%20you're%20able%20to%20get%20through%20the%20day%20without%20having%20to%20have%20a%20nap%2C%20well%2C%20then%20you%20had%20enough%20sleep%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2206ea9584-969e-4334-af20-71f35680562c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20tests%20don't%20make%20a%20better%20doctor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EO'Sullivan%20also%20addressed%20the%20rise%20of%20preventative%20testing.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffull-body-mri-save-your-life-or-waste-of-money-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFull-body%20MRIs%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20cost%20up%20to%20%242%2C500%20and%20genetic%20tests%20are%20among%20those%20increasingly%20offered%20by%20longevity%20clinics%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20more%20traditional%20healthcare%20settings.%20But%20health%20experts%20have%20split%20opinions%20about%20their%20effectiveness.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20argue%20there%20is%20value%20in%20tracking%20health%20data%20to%20notice%20conditions%20early.%20But%20O'Sullivan%20said%20tests%20can%20make%20a%20patient%20feel%20listened%20to%20and%20make%20a%20doctor%20feel%20protected%20from%20making%20mistakes%2C%20but%20they%20also%20have%20cons%2C%20like%20showing%20false-positives.%20And%20because%20equipment%20has%20become%20so%20advanced%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20a%20test%20may%20flag%20early%20signs%20of%20a%20disease%20that%20never%20causes%20symptoms%20or%20requires%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLearn%20to%20recognize%20what%20good%20medicine%20looks%20like%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Sullivan%20said%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20explain%20your%20problem%20to%20the%20doctor.%20You%20feel%20like%20they've%20taken%20the%20time%20to%20listen%20and%20understand%20and%20give%20you%20an%20explanation%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EO'Sullivan%20recommended%20having%20evidence-backed%20screenings%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-mild-cramps-colon-cancer-diagnosed-colonoscopy-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroutine%20colonoscopies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20cervical%20cancer%20screenings%20at%20the%20officially%20recommended%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGo%20to%20your%20doctor%20for%20the%20proper%20types%20of%20screening%20that%20are%20offered%20by%20standard%20health%20services%2C%20and%20don't%20do%20any%20extras%2C%20because%20somebody%20is%20making%20money%20out%20of%20making%20you%20anxious%20about%20your%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Sullivan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctor-use-fitness-trackers-obsessed-health-metric-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776957504000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ea1ce23fecbb42897a319d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctor-use-fitness-trackers-obsessed-health-metric-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Measuring%20our%20health%20data%20with%20wearable%20tech%20is%20more%20popular%20than%20ever.%20But%20a%20doctor%20said%20a%20lot%20of%20products%20make%20money%20from%20out%20health%20anxieties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kschewitz%40businessinsider.com%20(Kim%20Schewitz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctor-use-fitness-trackers-obsessed-health-metric-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Warner%20Bros%20Shareholders%20Approve%20Paramount's%20%2481%20Billion%20Takeover%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Per%20a