the%20U.S.%20Navy%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20oil%20market%20could%20remain%20distorted%20long%20after%20the%20Iran%20war%20ends%2C%20David%20Roche%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20bearish%20strategist%20thinks%20the%20world%20is%20facing%20a%2010%25%20energy%20supply%20shortage%20even%20with%20a%20peace%20deal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20lack%20of%20available%20supply%20could%20cause%20the%20world%20economy%20to%20contract%20by%203%25%2C%20he%20estimated.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Foil-prices%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOil%20markets%3C%2Fa%3E%20aren't%20going%20back%20to%20normal%20even%20when%20the%20US%20and%20Iran%20hammer%20out%20a%20lasting%20peace%20deal%2C%20according%20to%20one%20permabear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Roche%2C%20a%20strategist%20at%20Quantum%20Strategy%20who%20is%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BDr.%20Doom%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20persistently%20bearish%20calls%20on%20markets%20and%20the%20economy%2C%20said%20he%20believed%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-supply-shock-outlook-breaking-point-global-crude-supply-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupply%20disruptions%20in%20the%20oil%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0could%20persist%20long%20after%20the%20Iran%20war%20officially%20ended.%20That's%20because%20flows%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftensions-are-rising-the-strait-of-hormuz-ship-traffic-slowing-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStrait%20of%20Hormuz%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20unlikely%20to%20revert%20back%20to%20normal%20even%20after%20the%20conflict%20ends%20%E2%80%94%20a%20problem%20he%20thinks%20could%20spark%20energy%20shortages%20and%20dent%20global%20economic%20growth%20in%20a%20few%20months'%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20US%20has%20asked%20Iran%20to%20reopen%20the%20Strait%2C%20Tehran%20is%20unlikely%20to%20completely%20loosen%20its%20grip%20on%20the%20critical%20shipping%20passage%2C%20Roche%20said.%20Controlling%20the%20Strait%20gives%20the%20nation%20power%20over%20other%20Gulf%20countries%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoche%20also%20pointed%20to%20Iran's%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-blockade-hormuz-iran-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etolling%20of%20ships%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0passing%20through%20the%20Strait%2C%20another%20reason%20global%20supplies%20could%20remain%20crimped%20after%20the%20conflict%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20the%20US%20were%20to%20declare%20%26quot%3Bvictory%26quot%3B%20and%20exit%20the%20region%2C%20the%20world%20will%20likely%20face%20a%2010%25%20supply%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-iran-war-energy-crisis-iea-supply-shock-hormuz-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshortage%20in%20oil%20and%20gas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Roche%20estimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tankers%20would%20not%20flow%20the%20same%20way%20as%20they%20should.%20The%20oil%20would%20not%20flow%20the%20same%20way.%20Why%3F%20Because%20by%20going%20home%2C%20the%20US%20would%20leave%20Iran%20and%20the%20IRGC%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20Gulf.%20And%20then%2C%20only%20the%20ships%20that%20they%20like%20or%20who%20pay%20them%20enough%20will%20export%20oil%2C%26quot%3B%20Roche%20said%2C%20speaking%20to%20CNBC%20on%20Wednesday%20about%20his%20outlook%20for%20the%20oil%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20actually%2C%20that%20solution%20is%20not%20a%20solution%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%20of%20a%20US-Iran%20peace%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoche%20said%20he%20sees%20the%20oil%20shock%20moving%20into%20a%20new%20phase%2C%20in%20which%20consumers%20will%20start%20to%20feel%20the%20pain%20of%20actual%20oil%20and%20gas%20shortages%20beyond%20simply%20paying%20higher%20prices%20at%20the%20pump.%20That%20could%20hit%20the%20global%20economy%20as%20people%20have%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20pull%20back%20on%20consumption%2C%20he%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20last%20%26quot%3Bnormalized%26quot%3B%20tankers%20leaving%20the%20Gulf%20have%20likely%20already%20reached%20their%20final%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20fuel%20could%20cause%20global%20GDP%20to%20decline%20by%203%25%20in%20several%20months'%20time%2C%20he%20estimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20more%20on%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20oil%20supplies%20from%20the%20Gulf.%20%26quot%3BSo%20essentially%2C%20the%20pipeline%20is%20dry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20have%20rebounded%20sharply%20on%20hopes%20that%20a%20resolution%20is%20coming%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20particularly%20as%20the%20US%20and%20Iran%20have%20extended%20their%20ceasefire%20deadline%20this%20week.%20But%20negotiations%20to%20end%20the%20war%20are%20still%20ongoing%2C%20and%20the%20timeline%20for%20a%20formal%20peace%20deal%20remains%20uncertain%2C%20with%20President%20Trump%20saying%20on%20Tuesday%20he%20was%20waiting%20on%20a%20proposal%20from%20Iran%20to%20end%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-world-recession-economic-outlook-oil-gas-supply-shock-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776957130000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ea36b3367066d7c29701a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-world-recession-economic-outlook-oil-gas-supply-shock-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Permabear%20David%20Roche%20says%20he%20thinks%20the%20world%20is%20facing%20a%2010%25%20oil%20and%20gas%20shortage%20even%20with%20an%20Iran%20war%20peace%20deal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40businessinsider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-world-recession-ec