e%20way.%20I%20spoke%20with%20NYC%20dermatologists%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drhadleyking.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Hadley%20King%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zeichnerdermatology.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Joshua%20Zeichner%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20blackheads%20and%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20treat%20them%2C%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20provide%20their%20top%20product%20recommendations.%20Perhaps%20the%20most%20important%20tip%3F%20Blackheads%20(and%20visible%20pores%20in%20general)%20are%20completely%20normal%2C%20and%20it's%20impossible%20to%20totally%20prevent%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22622b48c7-b5c6-4e49-a9b8-a74d0d9ce58e%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20blackheads%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22How%20to%20Safely%20Remove%20Blackheads%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f7caf5494fce90018f7b6c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EThamKC%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20natural%20to%20assume%20that%20the%20dark%20appearance%20of%20blackheads%20is%20due%20to%20a%20buildup%20of%20dirt%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20quite%20the%20case.%20%26quot%3BBlackheads%20form%20when%20a%20pore%20becomes%20clogged%20with%20dead%20skin%20cells%20and%20oil%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20King.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20this%20material%20becomes%20oxidized%20by%20exposure%20to%20air%20it%20appears%20black%20%E2%80%94%20hence%20the%20name%20'blackhead'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlackheads%20commonly%20form%20on%20the%20areas%20of%20the%20face%20that%20produce%20more%20oil%2C%20such%20as%20the%20forehead%2C%20nose%2C%20and%20chin%20(also%20known%20as%20the%20t-zone).%20They%20can%20also%20appear%20inside%20the%20conchal%20bowl%20of%20the%20ears%2C%20as%20well%20as%20on%20the%20shoulders%2C%20back%2C%20and%20chest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20causes%20of%20blackheads%2C%20says%20Dr.%20Zeichner%2C%20is%20genetics.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20there%20are%20some%20external%20predisposing%20factors%20that%20can%20be%20controlled%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20adds.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20that%20stress%20and%20your%20diet%20can%20cause%20breakouts.%20Skim%20milk%20and%20foods%20with%20a%20high%20sugar%20load%20promote%20inflammation%20and%20oil%20production%2C%20as%20does%20stress.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2209506fef-fdd5-4d5b-a1e1-cc15616f8e9a%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20remove%20blackheads%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGood%20news%3A%20there%20are%20safe%20ways%20to%20remove%20blackheads%20at%20home%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20must%20be%20done%20properly%20to%20avoid%20irritation%2C%20scarring%2C%20or%20even%20infection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESqueezing%20blackheads%20out%20with%20your%20fingers%20might%20be%20one%20of%20the%20more%20satisfying%20ways%20to%20remove%20them%2C%20but%20Dr.%20King%20warns%20that%20it's%20not%20a%20good%20idea.%20%26quot%3BSqueezing%20blackheads%20can%20traumatize%20the%20skin%2C%20introduce%20bacteria%20and%20damage%20the%20pore%2Cwhich%20can%20spread%20debris%20and%20bacteria%20deeper%20into%20the%20tissue%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20King%20recommends%20trying%20any%20blackhead-removal%20technique%20after%20a%20warm%20shower%20or%20steaming%20the%20skin.%20This%20helps%20to%20soften%20the%20skin%20and%20the%20material%20that%20has%20collected%20in%20the%20pores.%20It's%20also%20important%20to%20gently%20cleanse%20the%20area%20before%20and%20after%20extraction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22How%20to%20Safely%20Remove%20Blackheads%20-%20Tweezerman%20Blackhead%20Extractor%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f7ca8f0282c500018c78e64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETweezerman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c045bce8-692d-4061-9d27-6cfcd7e58790%5C%22%3EManual%20removal%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20comedone%20extractor%20tool%20is%20one%20way%20to%20safely%20remove%20blackheads.%20The%20small%20loop%20on%20the%20end%20of%20a%20metal%20rod%20gently%20retracts%20the%20skin%20around%20the%20blackhead%2C%20bringing%20the%20contents%20to%20the%20surface.%20Dr.%20King%20recommends%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126294599o1-20%26h%3D80ddfe5eca7e2b8492b3489eb4852e3f94cc11180cba9f756c5f154f4e4356e6%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f4929e%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Fhow-to-remove-blackheads%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fgp%252Fproduct%252FB07NS4LTQ1%252Fref%253Das_li_tl%253Fie%253DUTF8%2526amp%253Btag%253Dbiip_100620_how-to-remove-blackheads-20%2526amp%253Bcamp%253D1789%2526amp%253Bcreative%253D9325%2526amp%253BlinkCode%253Das2%2526amp%253BcreativeASIN%253DB07NS4LTQ1%2526amp%253BlinkId%253Dfea32968a9e9170c619a4ad4dd699440%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20easy-to-use%20extractor%20from%20Tweezerman%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BUnlike%20squeezing%2C%20the%20comedone%20extractor%20does%20not%20compress%20the%20sides%20of%20the%20pore%2C%20so%20there%20is%20less%20risk%20of%20breaking%20the%20pore%20walls%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20King%20says.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20tissue%20damage%20may%20still%20occur%20so%20it's%20important%20to%20be%20very%20careful%20if%20you're%20attempting%20this%20at%20home.%26quot%3B%20Apply%20light%20pressure%2C%20and%20if%20nothing%20is%20coming%20up%2C%20don't%20keep%20trying%20(no%20matter%20how%20tempting%20it%20may%20be).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPore%20strips%20are%20a%20classic%20method%20of%20blackhead%20removal%3B%20it's%20eye-watering%20removal%20elicits%20memories%20of%20slumber%20party%20%26quot%3Bspa%26quot%3B%20treatments%20and%20rom-com%20makeover%20montages.%20Little%20did%20our%20tween%20selves%20know%20that%20pore%20strips%20should%20NOT%20feel%20as%20though%20we'd%20ripped%20a%20layer%20of%20skin%20off.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20to%20not%20leave%20the%20strips%20on%20for%20too%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20King%20warns.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20strip%20has%20completely%20dried%20it's%20more%20likely%20to%20traumatize%20and%20tear%20the%20skin%20when%20it%20gets%20peeled%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20notes%20that%20pore%20strips%20only%20temporarily%20remove%20the%20top%20layer%20of%20dead%20skin%20cells%20and%20blackheads%E2%80%94%20they're%20useless%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20preventing%20buildup.%20Still%2C%20they%20can%20be%20a%20great%2C%20time-efficient%20solution%20when%20you're%20in%20a%20pinch.%20Dr.%20King%20recommends%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126294599o1-20%26h%3Dfd430c9a81d366ffa2b21a46abd565615cc14b95081d12130007465b6a1701ef%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f4929e%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Fhow-to-remove-blackheads%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgoto.target.com%252Fc%252F196318%252F81938%252F2092%253Fu%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fwww.target.com%25252Fp%25252Fbiore-deep-cleansing-pore-strips-nose-14ct%25252F-%25252FA-12174329%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBiore%20Deep%20Cleansing%20Pore%20Strips%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126294599o1-20%26h%3D608eab44f977e04bd4089d165ba9da1db655dae258ffa2d6701d6be0210348a9%26postID%3D61b8efdbf2a36b1ac9f4929e%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Fhow-to-remove-blackheads%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.anrdoezrs.net%252Flinks%252F6415797%252Ftype%252Fdlg%252Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.dermstore.com%252Fproduct_Pore%252BPurifying%252BBlack%252BCharcoal%252BStrips%252B_76397.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBoscia%20Pore%20Purifying%20Black%20Charcoal%20Strips%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fshop-links.co%2F1720134564285697240%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeace%20Out%20Pore%20Treatment%20Strips%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222dc2b75a-267b-4b48-9279-54b8ebcb4bd2%5C%22%3EScrubs%20and%20retinoids%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22How%20to%20Remove%20Blackheads%20-%20Ghost%20Democracy%20Transparent%20Cleanser%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f7cb369282c500018c78ebd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGhost%20Democracy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20deeper%20cleanse%20with%20longer-lasting%20results%2C%20Dr.%20King%20and%20Dr.%20Zeichner%20recommends%20salicylic%20acid%20and%20topical%20retinoids.%20%26quot%3BSalicylic%20acid%20is%20an%20excellent%20pore-clearing%20ingredient%20because%20it%20exfoliates%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20skin%20and%20penetrates%20into%20pores%20to%20remove%20oil%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20King%20says.%20%26quot%3BThis%20helps%20to%20prevent%20pores%20from%20becoming%20clogged%20and%20can%20help%20remove%20clogs%20that%20have%20already%20formed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeta%20hydroxy%20acids%20(or%20BHAs)%20like%20salicylic%20acid%20are%20effective%20at%20pore-clearing%20because%20they%20dissolve%20the%20bonds%20that%20hold%20dull%2C%20dead%20skin%20cells%20on%20the%20surface%2C%20revealing%20smoother%2C%20brighter%20skin.%20BHAs%20are%20also%20oil-soluble%2C%20making%20it%20a%20great%20option%20for%20those%20with%20oily%20or%20acne-prone%20skin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20King%20highly%20recommends%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20