%252Ftiktok-kiss-falscara-lash-kit-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FKISS-Falscara-Eyelash-Starter-Kit%252Fdp%252FB082MQP2D7%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKISS%20Falscara%20Lengthening%20Lash%20Starter%20Kit%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20getting%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20includes%20all%20the%20products%20needed%20to%20apply%20individual%20lashes%2C%20from%20wisps%20to%20eyelash%20glue.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20tried%20the%20kit%20for%20myself%20and%20have%20yet%20to%20make%20a%20lash%20appointment%20since.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20TikTok%20is%20not%20to%20be%20credited%20for%20the%20popularity%20of%20individual%20lash%20extensions%2C%20I%20have%20the%20app%20to%20thank%20for%20all%20the%20lash%20hacks%20I've%20learned%20along%20the%20way.%20Because%20monthly%20trips%20to%20lash%20technicians%20can%20get%20expensive%2C%20TikTok%20creators%20have%20been%20posting%20ways%20their%20followers%20can%20manipulate%20lash%20strips%20to%20emulate%20the%20signature%20inward%20curve%20of%20individual%20clusters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20cut%20their%20strips%20into%20chunks%20and%20apply%20them%20one%20by%20one%2C%20while%20others%20use%20their%20lash%20curler%20to%20stamp%20their%20strips%20repeatedly%20until%20each%20strand%20sprouts%20upward%20and%20fans%20outward.%20Still%20on%20the%20hunt%20for%20the%20right%20hack%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20time%20to%20check%20out%20the%20hashtag%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2Famp%2Ftag%2Ffalscara%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%23falscara%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20kept%20popping%20up%20on%20my%20feed.%20Today%2C%20%23falscara%20has%20racked%20up%20over%2099%20million%20views%2C%20and%20at%20least%20100%20of%20those%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20me.%20This%20is%20where%20I%20discovered%20the%20KISS%20Falscara%20Lash%20Kit.%20When%20I%20saw%20the%20wisps%20resembled%20the%20same%20ones%20used%20by%20my%20lash%20technician%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhat's%20included%20in%20the%20KISS%20Falscara%20Lash%20Kit%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%20images%20of%20the%20product%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62aa066a8eacc300192dd445%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20kit%20comes%20with%20everything%20you%20need%2C%20including%20an%20applicator%20and%20glue.%3Cp%3EKayla%20Bickham%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-56044-20%26h%3D0dbf3109f869db8f825671f63b12ccdee0bf2e90ff11a6d93fcea148ea8aecc4%26postID%3D62aa047d17a7fe0c603af3a6%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Ftiktok-kiss-falscara-lash-kit-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FKISS-Falscara-Eyelash-Starter-Kit%252Fdp%252FB082MQP2D7%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKISS%20Falscara%20Eyelash%20Starter%20Kit%3C%2Fa%3E%20includes%2010%20wisps%20of%20varying%20lengths%20which%20makes%20each%20look%20customizable.%20It%20also%20comes%20with%20two%20types%20of%20applicator%20glue%3A%20The%20Falscara%20Eyelash%20Bond%20%26amp%3B%20Seal%20is%20geared%20toward%20daily%20applications%20while%20the%20Falscara%20Overnight%2010-Day%20Sealer%20is%20for%20extended%20wear.%20The%20purple%20and%20blue%20metal%20applicator%20provides%20a%20steady%20hand%20and%20ensures%20precise%20execution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EBefore%20and%20after%20applying%20the%20lashes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Profile%20shot%20of%20author%20before%20application%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62aa06d71c77440019597e20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22902%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBefore%3A%20My%20natural%20lashes%20before%20using%20the%20KISS%20Falscara%20Lash%20Kit.%3Cp%3EKayla%20Bickham%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20lashes%20are%20fine%20and%20short%20which%20has%20always%20caused%20issues%20for%20me%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20individual%20lash%20extensions.%20I've%20been%20told%20that%20the%20falsies%20have%20a%20hard%20time%20latching%20to%20my%20natural%20lashes%20because%20they%20are%20simply%20too%20heavy%20for%20them.%20With%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20I%20applied%20a%20generous%20amount%20of%20the%20Bond%20%26amp%3B%20Seal.%20Unlike%20lash%20strips%20that%20go%20on%20top%20of%20the%20lash%20line%2C%20these%20wisps%20are%20made%20to%20go%20underneath%20lashes.%20They're%20designed%20this%20way%20to%20look%20natural%20and%20feel%20comfortable%2C%20and%20I%20can%20attest%20that%20they%20do%20just%20that.%20After%20using%20the%20applicator%20to%20apply%20the%20longer%20lashes%20in%20my%20outer%20corner%20and%20the%20shorter%20lengths%20towards%20my%20inner%20tear%20duct%2C%20the%20fit%20was%20nearly%20perfect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Front%20facing%20shot%20of%20final%20look%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62aa07098eacc300192dd46b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22902%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAfter%3A%20I%20was%20able%20to%20get%20the%20look%20I%20wanted%20on%20the%20first%20try.%3Cp%3EKayla%20Bickham%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20it%20took%20multiple%20appointments%20for%20my%20lash%20tech%20to%20find%20the%20right%20formula%20that%20fit%20my%20eye%20shape%20and%20achieve%20the%20exact%20look%20I%20had%20in%20mind.%20With%20the%20kit%2C%20it%20took%20me%20one%20try%20to%20customize%20the%20look%20to%20my%20liking.%20The%20application%20takes%20some%20getting%20used%20to%20at%20first%2C%20but%20I%20recommend%20using%20one%20hand%20to%20press%20the%20top%20lashes%20upward%20onto%20the%20eyelid%20so%20the%20waterline%20is%20exposed.%20That%20way%20you%20can%20sit%20the%20lashes%20exactly%20where%20you%20need%20them.%20To%20seal%20the%20deal%2C%20I%20go%20over%20the%20top%20and%20bottom%20of%20my%20lashes%20with%20the%20bond%20one%20more%20time%20to%20comb%20my%20natural%20and%20false%20lashes%20together%20as%20one.%20When%20it's%20time%20to%20re-up%20up%20on%20wisps%2C%20which%20are%20also%20sold%20separately%2C%20I'll%20even%20use%20the%20bond%20for%20strip%20lashes%20in%20the%20meantime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EMy%20tips%20for%20removing%20the%20lashes%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20using%20the%20Falscara%20Overnight%2010%20Day%20Sealer%2C%20I've%20never%20made%20it%20beyond%20day%20three.%20For%20lashes%20as%20fine%20and%20irritable%20as%20mine%2C%20I%20expected%20as%20much.%20But%20since%20the%20kit%20comes%20with%20several%20wisps%20and%20glue%20in%20a%20tube%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20touch%20up%20here%20and%20there%20to%20stretch%20the%20longevity%20of%20the%20lashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20there's%20Falscara%20Remover%20that%20can%20be%20bought%20separately%2C%20I%20swear%20by%20micellar%20water.%20There's%20nothing%20that%20has%20worked%20faster%20or%20better%20at%20breaking%20down%20stubborn%20sticky%20spots%20on%20my%20lashes.%20No%20matter%20the%20removal%20product%20or%20how%20careful%20I%20am%2C%20I%20still%20find%20three%20to%20four%20of%20my%20temperamental%20lashes%20in%20the%20sink.%20Still%2C%20I'm%20willing%20to%20exchange%20a%20few%20loose%20lashes%20for%20a%20professional%20look%20without%20the%20price%20right%20from%20my%20own%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Ftiktok-kiss-falscara-lash-kit-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776956405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62