ndia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Ftamil-nadu-elections-the-optics-deficit-will-missing-stalin-rahul-brotherhood-hurt-alliance%2Farticleshow%2F130471890.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20absence%20of%20joint%20rallies%20between%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20alliance%20partners%20like%20MK%20Stalin%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20raises%20concerns%20about%20Congress's%20coalition%20strategy.%20This%20visual%20gap%20fuels%20speculation%20and%20opposition%20attacks%2C%20contrasting%20with%20proactive%20alliance%20building%20seen%20from%20other%20INDIA%20bloc%20leaders%20like%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22PALLAVI%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20asked%20a%20dermatologist%20to%20critique%20my%20skin-care%20routine%20%E2%80%94%20here's%20what%20I%20learned%2C%20plus%20products%20she%20recommended%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221201%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dermatologist%204x3%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c6d921926289807c8569eb2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22901%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThese%20are%20some%20of%20my%20go-to%20skin-care%20products.%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Lee%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20asked%20a%20celebrity%20dermatologist%2C%20Dr.%20Dendy%20Engelman%2C%20to%20go%20over%20my%20skin-care%20routine%20with%20a%20fine-tooth%20comb%20to%20show%20me%20what%20I'm%20doing%20right%2C%20and%20what%20I'm%20doing%20wrong.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBelow%2C%20Dr.%20Engelman%20uses%20my%C2%A0routine%20as%20a%20template%20to%20offer%20product%20recommendations%20and%20helpful%20advice%20on%20how%20to%20make%20sure%20your%20products%20actually%20work%20together.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20I've%20been%20lucky%20to%20work%20in%20a%20field%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-french-pharmacy-skincare-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erequires%20me%20to%3C%2Fa%3E%20spend%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Faffordable-skin-care-brands-companies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20extensive%20amount%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2F10-step-korean-skincare-routine-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etime%20researching%3C%2Fa%3E%20skin-care%20products%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fmaelove-skin-care-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20then%20testing%20them%20out%20on%20myself%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20see%20what's%20worthwhile.%20Quickly%2C%20you%20get%20good%20at%20spotting%20the%20winners%20from%20just%20the%20ingredient%20lists%2C%20and%20you%20become%20more%20adept%20at%20addressing%20your%20skin's%20needs%20as%20they%20arise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20back%20in%20the%20day%2C%20I%20was%20a%20high%20schooler%20dealing%20with%20my%20first%20round%20of%20acne%20that%20couldn't%20be%20solved%20by%20what%20my%20mother%20recommended%3A%20freshly%20washed%20sheets%2C%20a%20simple%20face%20wash%2C%20and%20drinking%20more%20water.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20I%20just%20wanted%20someone%20to%20put%20my%20skin-care%20routine%20under%20a%20microscope%2C%20and%20explain%20to%20me%20in%20plain%20English%20why%20things%20weren't%20working.%20But%20the%20expense%20of%20dermatology%20appointments%20meant%20the%20resource%20was%20more%20of%20a%20luxury.%20A%20new%20salicylic%20topical%20treatment%20from%20CVS%20was%20cheaper%20and%20more%20accessible%20than%20to%20pay%20for%20ongoing%20prescriptions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20things%20are%20different.%20My%20skin%20is%20mostly%20clear%2C%20and%20I%20have%20the%20privilege%20of%20visiting%20a%20dermatologist%20continually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20have%20the%20encouragement%20and%20resources%20to%20regularly%20discover%20solid%20products%2C%20rather%20than%20buying%20whichever%20has%20the%20best%20marketing%20campaign.%20But%2C%20I'm%20still%20human%2C%20and%20I%20regularly%20and%20knowingly%20cut%20corners%20with%20my%20own%20routine.%20I%20don't%20always%20follow%20best%20practices.%20Plus%2C%20even%20if%20what%20makes%20a%20good%20product%20actually%20%3Cem%3Egood%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20no%20longer%20a%20mystery%20to%20me%2C%20what%20makes%20a%20harmonious%20skin-care%20routine%20still%20is.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20myself%2C%20and%20anyone%20else%20reading%2C%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20construct%20a%20good%20skin-care%20routine%2C%20I%20asked%20a%20dermatologist%20to%20deconstruct%20my%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Dendy%20Engelman%20is%20a%20nationally%20acclaimed%20dermatologic%20surgeon%20and%20renown%20dermatologist.%20Previously%2C%20she's%20offered%20expertise%20and%20been%20interviewed%20as%20a%20celebrity%20dermatologist%20in%20publications%20such%20as%20Glamour%2C%20Vogue%2C%20and%20W%20Magazine.%20Currently%2C%20Dr.%20Engelman%20sees%20patients%20at%20MDCS%3A%20Manhattan%20Dermatology%20%26amp%3B%20Cosmetic%20Surgery%20and%20is%20a%20clinical%20assistant%20professor%20and%20director%20of%20dermatologic%20surgery%20at%20Metropolitan%20Hospital%20Center.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2224892add-c301-4966-bd8e-16204f97bd30%5C%22%3EBelow%2C%20you'll%20find%20Dr.%20Engelman's%20input%20on%20what%20I'm%20doing%20right%2C%20wrong%2C%20and%20which%20products%20she%20personally%20recommends.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EEvening%20routine%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22night%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c6d923f70a61e5d234c3334%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Lee%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigu