bing%20excess%20oils%2C%20but%20if%20you%20put%20it%20on%20for%20too%20long%2C%20you%20will%20notice%20your%20face%20becoming%20really%20dry.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20absorb%20excess%20oil%20but%20not%20absorb%20so%20much%20that%20your%20skin%20is%20dry%20and%20overcompensating%20by%20producing%20extra%20oil.%20Therefore%20the%20goal%20should%20not%20be%20to%20prolong%20the%20time%20the%20product%20is%20on%20your%20face%20but%20to%20stick%20to%20the%20recommended%20time%20or%20when%20you%20start%20to%20feel%20tightness%20from%20the%20mask%2C%20you%20should%20plan%20to%20rinse%20it%20off%20in%20two-five%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20I%20learned%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222501%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dermatologist%20products%20linedup%202x1%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c75be68262898073d2d3dcc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221251%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EShayanne%20Gal%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20I%20know%20sunscreen%20is%20the%20golden%20rule%20of%20any%20skin-care%20routine%2C%20but%20I've%20been%20overlooking%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20with%20the%20usual%20excuses%3A%20I%20don't%20spend%20much%20time%20outside%2C%20I%20always%20wear%20sunscreen%20for%20outdoor%20trips%2C%20and%20I%20hate%20the%20greasy%20feeling%20and%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20the%20absorb.%20However%2C%20Dr.%20Engelman%20says%20only%2010-15%20minutes%20a%20day%20is%20enough%20to%20add%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20While%20I%20do%20use%20serums%2C%20I%20definitely%20underestimated%20their%20importance.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Dr.%20Engelman%20calls%20them%20the%20%26quot%3Bworkhorse%20products%26quot%3B%20that%20deliver%20actives%20deep%20into%20the%20skin%20for%20specific%20concerns.%20Now%2C%20I'll%20make%20sure%20not%20to%20skip%20them%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20pay%20more%20attention%20to%20the%20serums%20built%20to%20target%20specific%20concerns%2C%20since%20they're%20the%20ones%20most%20capable%20of%20addressing%20them%20(think%3A%20fine%20lines%20and%20hyperpigmentation).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20I%20had%20also%20heard%20conflicting%20advice%20on%20whether%20I%20could%20layer%20moisturizers%20over%20my%20other%20products%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%20would%20it%20counteract%20what%20I%20just%20put%20on%20(and%20likely%20paid%20so%20much%20for)%3F%20Dr.%20Engelman%20says%20I%20should%20be%20layering%20a%20moisturizer%20over%20other%20(lighter)%20products%2C%20especially%20at%20night%20when%20the%20body's%20hydration%20is%20rebalancing.%20The%20skin%20can%20lose%20water%20while%20we%20sleep%2C%20but%20a%20serum%20and%20a%20cream%20at%20night%20can%20create%20a%20permeable%20seal%20so%20that%20whatever%20you%20have%20underneath%20can%20penetrate%20and%20hydrate.%20The%20only%20thing%20to%20avoid%20is%20layering%20BHAs%20and%20vitamin%20C%20over%20Differin%20%E2%80%94%20my%20retinol%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20I'll%20also%20be%20buying%20an%20overnight%20mask.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Dr.%20Engelman%20explained%20that%20while%20the%20body%20is%20in%20deep%2C%20restful%20sleep%2C%20the%20skin's%20metabolism%20increases%20%E2%80%94%20making%20cell%20turnover%20and%20renewal%20faster.%20Overnight%20masks%20support%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Lastly%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20more%20precise%20about%20how%20long%20I%20leave%20my%20clay%20mask%20on.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It's%20great%20at%20absorbing%20oil%2C%20but%20if%20it%20absorbs%20too%20much%20it%20can%20force%20the%20skin%20to%20compensate%20by%20becoming%20more%20oily%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dab06c1c-2883-4ae0-a715-01b8c25bbe5e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20the%20products%20Dr.%20Engelman%20recommended%20while%20critiquing%20my%20skin-care%20routine%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECleanser%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F