ink%20it's%20going%20to%20pay%20off%20in%20a%20very%20big%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20investments%20also%20come%20as%20Tesla%20pivots%20from%20a%20focus%20on%20traditional%20automotive%20sales%2C%20which%20typically%20have%20thin%20margins.%20Instead%2C%20the%20company%20is%20focusing%20on%20software-defined%20projects%20that%20could%20have%20higher%20margins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTesla%20is%20working%20on%20a%20lot%20of%20large%2C%20ambitious%20projects%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20during%20the%20call.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20all%20very%20challenging%2C%20but%20I%20think%20they're%20going%20to%20be%20revolutionary.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20at%20Tesla%20or%20have%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Abshimkus%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ebshimkus%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20on%20Signal%20at%20bshimkus.41.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20non-work%20device%2C%20and%20non-work%20WiFi%3B%20here's%20our%20guide%20to%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Esharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-mystery-ai-hardware-company-acquisition-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776956074000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ea215f367066d7c297009e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-mystery-ai-hardware-company-acquisition-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20single%20line%20in%20a%20new%20Tesla%20regulatory%20document%20says%20the%20co