%20Heritage%20Month%2C%20a%20time%20to%20recognize%20and%20celebrate%20the%20cultures%20and%20histories%20of%20Indigenous%20peoples%20across%20North%20America.%20While%20the%20month%20celebrates%20Native%20communities%2C%20it's%20also%20a%20time%20for%20raising%20awareness%20about%20the%20systemic%20issues%20Indigenous%20communities%20continue%20to%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20COVID%20definitely%20disproportionately%20impacted%20vulnerable%20groups%2C%20and%20now%20is%20a%20perfect%20time%20to%20be%20kind%20of%20raising%20awareness%20of%20those%20inequities%20and%20look%20for%20creative%20ways%20to%20be%20learning%20more%20about%20the%20people%20that%20we%20share%20the%20land%20with%2C%20but%20also%20to%20be%20supporting%20them%20whether%20that's%20through%20their%20businesses%20or%20through%20their%20other%20ventures%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Nicole%20McLaren%2C%20the%20owner%20and%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fravenreads.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERaven%20Reads%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20book%20subscription%20box%20that%20shares%20the%20voices%20and%20work%20of%20Indigenous%20authors%20while%20reinvesting%20money%20into%20other%20Indigenous-owned%20businesses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENovember%20is%20a%20great%20time%20to%20buy%20from%20Indigenous%20businesses%2C%20but%20by%20supporting%20these%20retailers%20year%20round%2C%20%26quot%3Byou're%20going%20to%20be%20providing%20not%20only%20revenue%20for%20that%20business%2C%20but%20you're%20building%20stronger%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20McLaren%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20put%20together%20a%20list%20of%20Native-owned%20businesses%20to%20consider%20when%20you're%20shopping%20for%20gifts%20or%20yourself.%20From%20jewelry%20to%20wine%2C%20there%20are%20lots%20of%20businesses%20to%20support%20with%20your%20dollars%2C%20especially%20during%20holidays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20ways%20to%20honor%20Native%20American%2