er%20took%20her%20away%20from%20her%20parenting.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Theresa%20Siller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20struggled%20to%20provide%20care%20for%20my%20mother%20and%20my%20youngest%20child%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELooking%20back%2C%20I%20wish%20that%20I%20had%20been%20able%20to%20find%20a%20better%20balance%20for%20my%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20know%20I%20did%20the%20best%20I%20could%2C%20and%20I%20appreciate%20my%20daughter%20for%20giving%20me%20grace%20over%20this.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20the%20evening%20well.%20My%20family%2C%20along%20with%20my%20mother%2C%20was%20enjoying%20buttery%20breadsticks%20and%20delicious%20salads%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folive-garden-meal-worth-the-money-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOlive%20Garden%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20awaiting%20our%20entr%C3%A9es.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWe%20treated%20ourselves%20to%20this%20special%20outing%2C%20prior%20to%20our%20youngest%20daughter%2C%20then%2011%2C%20facing%20kidney%20surgery%20the%20next%20day.%20Just%20as%20the%20chicken%20marsala%20and%20the%20linguine%20arrived%2C%20my%20mom's%20front%20tooth%20fell%20out.%20We%20quickly%20placed%20it%20into%20a%20protective%20baggie%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20address%20her%20need%20for%20dentistry%20the%20following%20day%2C%20since%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20would%20be%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20providing%20comfort%20to%20our%20nervous%20tween.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20moment%2C%20bewildered%2C%20I%20realized%20the%20untenable%20situation%20%E2%80%94%20my%20inability%20to%20meet%20my%20mother's%20and%20my%20daughter's%20needs%20simultaneously.%20It%20was%20then%20that%20I%20fully%20understood%20the%20emotional%20impact%20of%20being%20part%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsandwich-generation-mom-emotional-burnout-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esandwich%20generation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%2010%20years%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20helped%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongevity-tips-life-advice-octogenarian-friends-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoctogenarian%20mom%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20was%20low-vision.%20We%20were%20happy%20to%20be%20there%20for%20her%2C%20but%20it%20took%20a%20toll%20on%20us%2C%20especially%20our%20youngest%20daughter.%20Looking%20back%2C%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20been%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsandwich-generation-woman-caring-for-mother-and-son-getting-masters-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebalance%20everyone's%20needs%3C%2Fa%3E%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22891%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20(middle)%2C%20shown%20with%20her%20mother%20and%20three%20daughters.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7a5e83fecbb42897a2329%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(middle)%20said%20that%20caring%20for%20her%20mom%20often%20meant%20she%20missed%20out%20on%20some%20parts%20of%20parenting%20her%20youngest%20daughter.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Theresa%20Siller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2247ad4d7f-3cac-450d-965e-62b8cc8724e2%5C%22%3EMy%20responsibilities%20pulled%20me%20in%20two%20directions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mother%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F101-year-old-grandma-many-friends-secrets-building-community-social-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eadored%20all%20her%20grandkids%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20she%20seemed%20to%20hold%20a%20special%20place%20in%20her%20heart%20for%20my%20youngest.%20She%20affectionately%20called%20her%20%26quot%3BGrammy's%20little%20bobolink.%26quot%3B%20One%20time%2C%20while%20watching%20her%20on%20the%20trampoline%2C%20Mom%20smiled%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20poetry%20in%20motion.%26quot%3B%20When%20she%20became%20a%20tween%2C%20mom%20marveled%20at%20how%20%26quot%3Bself-assured%26quot%3B%20she%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20irony%20is%20not%20lost%20on%20me%20that%2C%20for%20all%20that%20love%20and%20high%20regard%20for%20her%20granddaughter%2C%20my%20mother%2C%20through%20no%20fault%20of%20her%20own%2C%20took%20me%20away%20from%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2208f422a8-224a-4531-9637-61de36b174a6%5C%22%3EHectic%20was%20just%20a%20way%20of%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom%20loved%20riding%20shotgun%20to%20the%20retinologist%2C%20dermatologist%2C%20internist%2C%20dentist%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20visit%20the%20bank%2C%20grocery%20store%2C%20hairdresser%2C%20church%2C%20and%20attend%20her%20many%20social%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20two%20older%20daughters%20embarked%20on%20their%20own%20busy%20lives%20as%20teenagers%20during%20this%20time%2C%20but%20our%20third%20daughter%20lost%20my%20presence%20at%20home%20while%20I%20was%20shuttling%20my%20mom%20to%20all%20of%20those%20appointments%20and%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20youngest%20has%20always%20been%20an%20old%20soul%2C%20independent%20and%20artistic.%20She'd%20rather%20be%20at%20home%20creating%20than%20waiting%20in%20the%20car%20or%20at%20a%20doctor's%20office.%20Once%2C%20I%20received%20a%20text%20from%20her%2C%20%26quot%3BWhere%20are%20you%3F%26quot%3B%20Rushed%20as%20usual%2C%20I%20had%20failed%20to%20write%20her%20a%20note%20explaining%20where%20I%20was%20and%20when%20I'd%20be%20returning.%20I%20am%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsandwich-generation-mom-balance-child-care-eldercare-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eawash%20with%20guilt%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20being%20gone%20so%20much%20from%20her%2C%20even%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e16d1dfc-0e8a-49e7-a9f0-a5c386da8a5a%5C%22%3EI%20know%20I%20did%20the%20best%20I%20could%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECan%20I%20get%20a%20do-over%3F%20No%2C%20I%20cannot.%20My%20mom%20needed%20our%20help%2C%20and%20I'm%20glad%20she%20could%20count%20on%20us.%20At%20times%20when%20I%20look%20back%20on%20those%20merry-go-round%20days%2C%20I%20am%20filled%20with%20melancholy%2C%20for%20the%20resulting%20quality%20time%20I%20know%20I%20lost%20with%20my%20youngest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20my%20mother%20is%20no%20longer%20with%20us%2C%20and%20my%20daughter%20is%20a%20talented%20clothing%20designer%20and%20a%20thriving%20college%20student.%20I%20have%20shared%20my%20sadness%20to%20her%20about%20my%20lack%20of%20presence%20at%20home%20while%20she%20was%20in%20her%20tweens.%20She%20has%20given%20me%20generous%20grace%20over%20this.%20I%20am%20hugely%20grateful%20for%20the%20relationship%20we%20have%2C%20even%20if%20I%20still%20regret%20having%20to%20split%20my%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjuggling-moms-care-daughters-childhood-hard-sandwich-generation-2026-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776955621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e7a4dd367066d7c296f229%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjuggling-moms-care-daughters-childhood-hard-sandwich-generation-2026-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20was%20glad%20I%20could%20show%20up%20for%20my%20mom%20when%20she%20needed%20me%2C%20but%20I%20still%20regret%20how%20often%20I%20wasn't%20there%20for%20my%20daughter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Theresa%20Siller)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjuggling-moms-care-daughters-childhood-hard-sandwich-generation-2026-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Put%203-year%20halt%20on%20H-1B%2C%20end%20H-4%3A%20New%20GOP%20bill%20by%20Rep%20Crane%20seeks%20major%20reforms%20in%20visa%20programs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776955617000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2F