.%3Cp%3ESurratt%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20to%20any%20flawless%20makeup%20look%20is%20a%20well-crafted%20makeup%20brush.%20A%20good%20brush%20is%20durable%2C%20distributes%20pigment%20evenly%2C%20and%20blends%20seamlessly%20without%20irritating%20the%20skin%20or%20causing%20patchiness.%20While%20different%20brushes%20are%20intended%20for%20different%20purposes%2C%20there%20aren't%20technically%20any%20hard%20and%20fast%20rules.%20The%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20to%20find%20what%20works%20for%20you%20and%20invest%20in%20quality%20brushes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20bristle%20softness%20is%20a%20major%20indicator%20of%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20feeling%20luxurious%2C%20the%20softest%20brushes%20will%20also%20help%20your%20makeup%20to%20look%20its%20best.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20they%20are%20natural%20hair%20or%20synthetic%2C%20you%20want%20something%20that%20feels%20soft%20to%20touch%20against%20the%20eyes%20and%20face%20%E2%80%94%20this%20will%20be%20key%20to%20blending%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20makeup%20artist%20and%20Stila%20Global%20Beauty%20Director%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcharlieriddle%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECharlie%20Riddle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BAny%20brush%20that%20is%20more%20coarse%20will%20make%20your%20makeup%20look%20more%20textured%20and%20difficult%20to%20blend.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20choosing%20brushes%2C%20it's%20also%20helpful%20to%20consider%20how%20often%20you'll%20use%20them.%20If%20you%20typically%20use%20makeup%20brushes%20daily%20or%20travel%20with%20them%20regularly%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20it%20to%20invest%20in%20high-quality%20ones.%20%26quot%3BI%20always%20look%20for%20quality%20because%20I%20wash%20them%20so%20often%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Los%20Angeles-based%20makeup%20artist%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftarrynfeldman%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETarryn%20Feldman%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220ad7a61e-949e-4a37-b940-17f42f74965b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20top%20picks%20for%20the%20best%20makeup%20brushes%2C%20according%20to%20makeup%20artists%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20best%20face%20brushes%3Cp%3EThis%20multitasking%20tool%20features%20a%20large%20fluffy%20brush%20on%20one%20end%20and%20a%20smaller%2C%20more%20precise%20brush%20on%20the%20other.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20dual%20ended%20brushes%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Riddle.%20%26quot%3BNot%20only%20are%20you%20getting%20two%20for%20one%20but%20this%20is%20great%20for%20buffing%20on%20a%20light%20foundation%20or%20cream%20products.%20I%20love%20to%20apply%20concealer%20or%20highlighter%20with%20the%20smaller%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20going%20to%20treat%20yourself%20to%20one%20luxury%20makeup%20brush%2C%20make%20it%20this%20one.%20%26quot%3BDefinitely%20a%20splurge%20but%20worth%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Riddle%20says%20of%20the%20fluffy%20face%20brush.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20so%20soft%20and%20perfect%20for%20applying%20powders.%20Every%20product%20goes%20on%20effortlessly%20with%20this%20brush.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECelebrity%20makeup%20artist%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fjamiebeaute%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJamie%20Dorman%3C%2Fa%3E%20recommends%20this%20brush%20due%20to%20its%20ultra-soft%20fibers%20that%20allow%20for%20flawless%20foundation%20application.%20%26quot%3BIts%20gentle%20bristles%20make%20for%20a%20glowing%2C%20skin-like%20finish%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20double-sided%20nature%20of%20this%20brush%20makes%20it%20suitable%20for%20both%20liquid%20or%20cream%20blush%20as%20well%20as%20other%20face%20products.%20%26quot%3BThe%20sponge%20end%20stipples%20on%20the%20product%20and%20the%20brush%20end%20can%20blend%20the%20edges%20and%20apply%20a%20powder%20blush%20on%20top%20for%20longevity%2C%26quot%3B%20Dorman%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20highlighter%20fanatic%2C%20this%20brush%20will%20make%20a%20great%20addition%20to%20your%20collection.%20The%20fluffy%20tapered%20end%20is%20ideal%20for%20diffusing%20liquid%20or%20powder%20highlighter%20as%20well%20as%20precise%20powder%20application%2C%20Dorman%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fluffy%20powder%20brush%20is%20perfect%20for%20diffused%2C%20natural-looking%20bronzer%20application.%20%26quot%3BIts%20soft%20edges%20prevent%20harsh%20lines%20and%20its%20tapered%20tip%20allows%20precise%20product%20placement%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dorman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20best%20eye%20%26amp%3B%20brow%20brushes%3Cp%3EEvery%20makeup%20collection%20needs%20a%20brow%20brush%2C%20and%20a%20double-sided%20one%20like%20this%20pick%20from%20Senna%20is%20ideal.%20Dorman%20loves%20how%20the%20dense%20angled%20brush%20side%20is%20fine%20enough%20to%20create%20hair-like%20strokes%20while%20the%20spoolie%20side%20is%20great%20for%20blending%20out%20harsh%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20eyeshadow%20brushes%20are%20created%20equal.%20%26quot%3B%5BThis%5D%20is%20the%20perfect%20brush%20if%20you%20have%20small%20eyes%2C%20not%20much%20lid%20space%2C%20or%20need%20a%20precisely%20placed%20crease%20shade%2C%26quot%3B%20Dorman%20says.%20%26quot%3BThe%20edges%20blend%20the%20placed%20line%20as%20you%20apply%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20staple%20among%20makeup%20artists%20and%20enthusiasts%20alike%2C%20the%20MAC%20217%20is%20what%20Dorman%20calls%20%26quot%3Bthe%20perfect%20shadow%20blending%20brush.%26quot%3B%20She%20continues%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20brush%20works%20for%20blending%20harsh%20shadow%2C%20applying%20a%20wash%20of%20color%2C%20or%20for%20applying%20lipstick%20like%20a%20stain.%20It%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20versatile%20brushes%20in%20my%20kit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENatural%20hair%20versus%20synthetic%20brushes%3Cp%3EMakeup%20brush%20bristles%20are%20available%20in%20three%20main%20categories%3A%20natural%2C%20synthetic%2C%20or%20a%20blend%20of%20the%20two.%20If%20you%20adhere%20to%20a%20vegan%20lifestyle%2C%20prefer%20vegan%20products%2C%20or%20have%20any%20allergies%20to%20animal%20hair%20that's%20used%20in%20natural%20brushes%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20stick%20with%20synthetic%20brushes.%20These%20are%20typically%20made%20from%20nylon%2C%20polyester%2C%20and%20other%20synthetic%20fibers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20natural%20and%20synthetic%20brushes%20can%20be%20beneficial%20for%20different%20reasons.%20%26quot%3BAnything%20natural%20hair%20is%20amazing%20for%20blending%3B%20eyes%2C%20blush%2C%20powder.%26quot%3B%20Riddle%20explains.%20%26quot%3BSynthetics%20are%20great%20for%20applying%20primers%2C%20foundations%2C%20concealers%2C%20contour.%20I%20wouldn't%20say%20one%20is%20better%20than%20the%20other%20%E2%80%94%20it%20really%20depends%20on%20the%20specific%20use%20of%20the%20brush.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-makeup-brushes%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1776955563000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658dea61ec62ab5daf7f6404%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-makeup-brushes%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Whether%20you%20realize%20it%20or%20not%2C%20brushes%20can%20make%20or%20break%20your%20makeup.%20We%20asked%20makeup%20artists%20to%20share%20the%20makeup%20brushes%20they%20recommend%20and%20use%20on%20their%20clients.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Santino)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-makeup-brushes%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2219%20luxury%20skincare%20buys%20that%20are%20worth%20the