er%2C%20their%20mother%20too%20was%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRelatives%2C%20instead%20of%20offering%20support%2C%20distanced%20themselves.%20We%20were%20only%20two%20daughters%2C%20and%20society%20was%20cruel%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rupam%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20told%20us%20we%20had%20no%20future%2C%20that%20we%20were%20helpless%20without%20parents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496969%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20in%20that%20moment%20of%20loss%20and%20abandonment%2C%20Rupam%20found%20the%20spark%20of%20a%20promise%20%E2%80%94%20to%20her%20mother%2C%20and%20to%20herself%3A%20%3Cem%3EI%20will%20do%20something%20big%20in%20life.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20at%20just%2022%2C%20she%20has%20kept%20that%20promise%20by%20clearing%20the%20Jharkhand%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(JPSC)%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20in%20her%20first%20attempt%2C%20without%20coaching%2C%20without%20guidance%2C%20and%20against%20all%20odds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20long%20road%20to%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20losing%20their%20parents%2C%20Rupam%20and%20her%20sister%20resolved%20to%20fight%20back%20instead%20of%20succumbing%20to%20despair.%20Finances%20were%20tight%2C%20and%20emotional%20support%20was%20absent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201